Powers.DescShort: Auto Res Placate, Disorient, Sleep, Smashing, Lethal, Fire, Cold, Toxic
Powers.DescLong: Demonlings are resistant to Placate and Disorient effects.  They are also resistant to Lethal, Smashing, Fire, Cold and Toxic damage.  They can also use Corruption on their foes.
Two quick Swipes with your claws. Does minor lethal damage, but has a quick recharge rate. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Very Fast
You Slash at your foe with your claws, dealing a good amount of lethal and toxic damage. This attack also has a chance to knock down an enemy. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Fast

Powers.DescShort: Ranged, Minor DMG(Fire), Foe Minor DoT (Toxic), -Res
Powers.DescLong: You fire a bolt of hellfire corrupting your victim's very living essence dealing minor toxic damage as well as reducing their damage resistance for a short time. Damage: Minor Recharge: Very Fast
